metadata.name: Misty Morning
metadata.description:
Image 1/6 "Misty Morning

This picture was taken on a misty morning on Charles Bridge in Prague.
It was 8 o'clock in the morning and I was looking for exciting motifs for my photo series.
This silence on this morning was indescribable, there were very few people besides me on the spot at this time.
I went up and down the bridge and in my ears was the music of the street musicians at this time already whistled into their musical instruments.
Really an impressive morning which enticed me to shoot this picture.

The buyer gets a photo print in size 40x60
